title.label: Can’t play unless I supply email

content.label: I haven’t played for awhile. I upgraded today and the app won’t let me play unless I give them my email address, which will undoubtedly lead to spam. No thank you!
I loved watching the advert but when I started this free game, it said I had to join the club, which requires a payment, in order to play.  That’s pretty sneaky.
Thank you for bringing new life to this great game!  It’s easy, it’s addicting, but can easily be put down and picked back up again if playing is interrupted.  Love it!
The title says it all. This is unplayable without buying a subscription.

very fun game, very clean UI.  nicely done!

but i only ever get 50-60% of claimed daily word count.   would be MUCH better if:
1- view a list of words you didn't find
2- get definitions of words you didn't find, or made accidentally
Wish I knew how people get such high scores, though.
It is the most challenging and most interesting apps I have ever used. It's so interesting that often times I skip some important events to play the game. It's  so addictive!!!!!!!

Love this game and have been playing it for a long time but lately it seems to crash more and more. Usually when it crashes I have gotten close to finding all the words and when it reloads I have lost all my points and credit for the words I had found.
I'd love more puzzle packs. Please, please, please add more and update this app. Thanks!

title.label: Love it love it love it

content.label: Addicting!  I love that there are more packages! It's very challenging, frustrating AND addicting.  Only reason NOT 5 stars----  when the circled letter is a hard one like Z or X I can figure out the "bonus word" that uses all 9 letters but I cannot make enough words to complete that board.

This is such a great game!  It makes you think and it's very addicting.  I love playing it and I would certainly recommend it to anyone who loves the combination of words and a challenge.  The daily puzzles are great.  I don't mind paying for new word packs because they are nominally priced, however when all of the available packs are completed there needs to be more -- several more.  Please considering adding a few new packs.  Then I would give this game six stars if it were possible.

Really good, but sometimes the selection circle will stick on one letter, making it impossible to score words using that letter. 

For example, I wanted to spell 'BELTS', but since the selection circle was stuck on the letter A, I couldn't spell it. How can this be fixed? It's happened to me in multiple levels.
I love that there's a new challenge every day. Always fun.
Great game--hope you'll be adding more categories and levels soon.
I enjoy playing this game it helps you to stimulate your thinking process
Really good brain massages.
Simple concept but fun word game.
Easy to learn like playing with fridge magnets
Addictive
I loved this app...can't use it now.
The desire to get better at this make-a-word game is irresistible.

title.label: I love it but I don't understand how to move on

content.label:
I love this game but I'm stuck on my first set of words with no idea how to move on to the next. The "menu" says I have found 45/45 words but the game doesn't end and there's been no additional feedback. 

Subtracting one star for confusion.

Pretty please?

LOVE THIS GAME!!!!

title.label: Best word game I've ever played

content.label: Holy crap.
Shuffling letters smooth as silk, speed challenges for the most daring, makes thinking FUN! Warning: Once begun, very difficult to stop - keep device charger handy!!!
Hands down one of the best word games out there! I especially love the "Daily Words" mini-game! :)
Lots of fun. I want more!!
Some of the daily words and occupations are strange but all in all it's a great game
Great word game. Its crazy addictive and my whole family loves playing it. Highly recommend this one. My fav game by far!

title.label: FUN word game. A must have!

content.label: Challenging and truly fun to play. Love the colors scoring system. Endless.
I have enjoyed this game.
One of the best word games I've seen!!!!!
I have so many app games, but this is really the only one I usually play it's that addicting!
Keep up the great work
Great fun trying to find ALL the words

Love it!  Even my kids join me now and then.  I am going to be bummed when I reach the end!
I am addicted to the daily game now...
My one time favorite game. Love it's word. challenges.  Keep up the good work.
Love the challenge of finding the word that uses all the letters

title.label: Awesome app for the word buff!

content.label: Seriously if your love a good time filler and up for a challenge, this is the game! I love trying to get all the words I can and striving to get the big word is somewhat challenging at times but so much fun!
One of my favorite games on the iPhone! Great fun for killing time waiting in doctors' offices, etc! Just need some more word packs!
I love this game! It is fun and challenging.  We need more puzzle packs!
It's one of my all time favorites and is a great way to keep your vocabulary up. I get so happy every time I see a new word pack is released. Please keep them coming!
This is one of the best word games I've played. Lots of fun!
Kids love it and I love it too. We play it together on iPad. Only gripe is in-app purchases. Dislike that.
Good pace. Good graphics and feedback. Fun to play.
Keeps you thinking. Enjoy this game
Tons of fun and more useful than the dorky games I usually play :-D
Great mind game! I use this in my 9th grade English classroom as a brain teaser when we have extra time. Worth the money!
This game is so addicting. From the first try until you just have to get some rest--you just cant stop playing.
Please make more & more of these games
